Package: ibrestr
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Brokers Rest API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mislav Sagovac
Maintainer: Mislav Sagovac <mislav.sagovac@contentio.biz>
Description: This R package provides a comprehensive R6 class-based interface 
    to the Interactive Brokers Client Portal API. It allows users to perform a 
    variety of operations such as trading, monitoring, and managing their 
    Interactive Brokers account directly from R. Key functionalities include 
    retrieving market data, executing and managing trades, handling portfolios, 
    and configuring email notifications for trading activities. The package 
    ensures secure communication with the API and is designed to facilitate easy
    integration for automated trading and financial analysis within the R environment.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
